!---- Чтение сортамента брусковых перемычек ---- dim naen_m_br[] : naen_m_br[1] = "" dim dlin_m_br[] dim max_pr_m_br[] dim tolsh_m_br[] dim vis_m_br[] dim nagr_m_br[] dim ves_m_br[] dim gost_m_br[] : gost_m_br[1] = "" ch3=OPEN("TEXT","перемычки.txt","SEPARATOR='\t',MODE=RO,LIBRARY") i = 1: n=1: j=1 : v0="" : v1=0 : v2=0 : v3=0 : v4=0 : v5=0 "nxt": if n <> -1 then n=INPUT(ch3,i,1,v0,v1,v2,v3,v4,v5) if vartype(v0)=2 then if STRSTR(v0,"-п")=0 then naen_m_br[j]=v0 dlin_m_br[j]=v1/1000 tolsh_m_br[j]=v2/1000 vis_m_br[j]=v3/1000 max_pr_m_br[j] = 0 nagr_m_br[j]=v4 ves_m_br[j]=v5 gost_m_br[j] = "ГОСТ 948-2016" j = j + 1 endif endif i = i + 1 goto "nxt" else close (ch3) endif if j>1 then PARAMETERS naen_m_br=naen_m_br PARAMETERS dlin_m_br=dlin_m_br PARAMETERS tolsh_m_br=tolsh_m_br PARAMETERS vis_m_br=vis_m_br PARAMETERS nagr_m_br=nagr_m_br PARAMETERS ves_m_br=ves_m_br PARAMETERS max_pr_m_br=max_pr_m_br PARAMETERS gost_m_br = gost_m_br endif !--------------------------------------------

"load_txt_pos": dstr = "" ch22 = OPEN ("DateTime", "", "%y%m%d%H%M%S") n = INPUT (ch22, "", "", dstr) CLOSE (ch22) ch4 = OPEN ("TEXT", dstr, "SEPARATOR=';', MODE = RO, DIALOG") n_load = 0 : err = 0 i = 1: n = 1 "nxt3": if n <> -1 then v0=0 : v1=0 : v2=0 n=INPUT(ch4,i,1,v0,v1,v2) if vartype(v1)=2 then if vartype(v0)=1 then v0 = str("%.0", v0) if vartype(v2)=1 then v2 = "" n_load = n_load + 1 t_pos[n_load] = v0 t_naen[n_load] = v1 t_obozn[n_load] = v2 endif i = i + 1 if i<10000 then goto "nxt3" endif close (ch4) return
"load_txt_mark": dstr = "" ch22 = OPEN ("DateTime", "", "%y%m%d%H%M%S") n = INPUT (ch22, "", "", dstr) CLOSE (ch22) ch4 = OPEN ("TEXT", dstr+"1", "SEPARATOR=';', MODE = RO, DIALOG") n_load = 0 : err = 0 i = 1: n = 1 "nxt4": if n <> -1 then v0=0 : v1=0 : v2=0 n=INPUT(ch4,i,1,v0,v1,v2) if vartype(v0)=2 then if vartype(v1)=1 then v1 = str("%.0", v1) if vartype(v2)=1 then v2 = str("%.0", v2) n_load = n_load + 1 t_chsum[n_load] = v0 t_otm[n_load] = v1 t_mark[n_load] = v2 endif i = i + 1 if i<10000 then goto "nxt4" endif close (ch4) return
